      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Looking for a budget-friendly project or a car with potential? This vehicle is ready for a new owner who doesn't mind rolling up their sleeves! While it shows significant wear and tear and will require some mechanical work and TLC to get back to its best, it's a fantastic opportunity to own a car at a very accessible price point. Perfect for a mechanic or a DIY enthusiast looking for their next challenge!",
